-*
-*  Gregorian Calendar to Modified Julian Date
-*
-*  Given:
-*     IY,IM,ID     int    year, month, day in Gregorian calendar
-*
-*  Returned:
-*     DJM          dp     modified Julian Date (JD-2400000.5) for 0 hrs
-*     J            int    status:
